or smoking,

860
00:39:59,100 --> 00:40:00,420
or gambling.

861
00:40:00,660 --> 00:40:02,500
You don’t even visit brothel.

862
00:40:03,420 --> 00:40:05,100
What do you like?

863
00:40:05,340 --> 00:40:06,940
You only love acting in the opera.

864
00:40:07,100 --> 00:40:08,980
When you got cut out in theater,

865
00:40:09,340 --> 00:40:11,220
your world collapsed.

866
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:14,220
Men should

867
00:40:15,260 --> 00:40:16,860
love more than one thing

868
00:40:16,860 --> 00:40:18,420
to divert attention.

869
00:40:18,580 --> 00:40:20,820
In this way, when one thing

870
00:40:20,820 --> 00:40:21,620
goes wrong,

871
00:40:22,140 --> 00:40:24,700
you can still enjoy other things.

872
00:40:24,700 --> 00:40:25,420
Right?

873
00:40:28,820 --> 00:40:30,620
I don’t like anything else.

874
00:40:35,100 --> 00:40:36,620
But I like delicious food.

875
00:40:38,140 --> 00:40:40,060
That’s easy.

876
00:40:40,380 --> 00:40:40,900
Guests.

877
00:40:41,060 --> 00:40:42,060
Here is your salted duck.

878
00:40:44,860 --> 00:40:46,620
All your dishes have been served.

879
00:40:49,740 --> 00:40:50,780
Could you give me a pot of tea?

880
00:40:50,780 --> 00:40:51,220
Okay.

881
00:40:51,220 --> 00:40:53,500
Xirui, are you happy now?

882
00:40:55,020 --> 00:40:55,860
Yes.

883
00:40:57,060 --> 00:40:58,220
That’s right.

884
00:40:58,540 --> 00:41:01,300
You should learn to have fun.

885
00:41:01,380 --> 00:41:03,380
Spend money extravagantly

886
00:41:03,540 --> 00:41:05,380
without a blink of an eye.

887
00:41:05,380 --> 00:41:06,700
How great it feels.

888
00:41:08,380 --> 00:41:09,820
We have made the money

889
00:41:09,820 --> 00:41:10,940
and become famous.

890
00:41:10,940 --> 00:41:12,380
If we don’t learn to enjoy it,

891
00:41:12,500 --> 00:41:14,860
our efforts won’t pay off.

892
00:41:15,900 --> 00:41:17,540
I feel great on stage.

893
00:41:18,180 --> 00:41:18,940
No.

894
00:41:20,460 --> 00:41:22,100
Nothing feels as great as when I’m on stage.

895
00:41:23,540 --> 00:41:24,700
Fine, I can’t talk you out of it.

896
00:41:24,700 --> 00:41:25,700
Let’s drink.

897
00:41:26,580 --> 00:41:27,460
Drink.

898
00:41:35,100 --> 00:41:36,180
It’s too cold out there.

899
00:41:43,220 --> 00:41:45,540
You come at a good time, Mr. Cheng.

900
00:41:45,900 --> 00:41:47,420
I have a book list.

901
00:41:47,420 --> 00:41:50,020
Please help me find these books.

902
00:41:54,020 --> 00:41:55,820
Those professional books have no Chinese versions

903
00:41:55,900 --> 00:41:56,860
and have few copies.

904
00:41:56,860 --> 00:41:58,380
I can’t find them in bookstore.

905
00:41:58,380 --> 00:42:00,700
Either new or second-hand will do.

906
00:42:00,700 --> 00:42:03,700
I can read both English and Russian.

907
00:42:05,220 --> 00:42:05,780
Okay.

908
00:42:07,060 --> 00:42:08,460
I can help you.

909
00:42:09,460 --> 00:42:10,460
Mr. Cheng.

910
00:42:11,540 --> 00:42:14,420
I came to save you despite the bad weather.

911
00:42:14,420 --> 00:42:16,020
You owe me.

912
00:42:16,660 --> 00:42:17,660
Of course.

913
00:42:17,660 --> 00:42:19,380
I don’t need you to repay any favor.

914
00:42:19,380 --> 00:42:20,580
I will pay you based on original price

915
00:42:20,580 --> 00:42:22,940
for the guns you give me.

916
00:42:23,420 --> 00:42:24,500
You won’t suffer loss.

917
00:42:25,140 --> 00:42:25,700
What do you think?

918
00:42:26,740 --> 00:42:27,740
Think about it.

919
00:42:30,180 --> 00:42:33,820
You call me Mr. Cheng all the time.

920
00:42:35,100 --> 00:42:37,220
I don’t think you regard me as a friend.

921
00:42:54,660 --> 00:42:55,820
What are you doing?

922
00:43:03,020 --> 00:43:04,140
Uncle.

923
00:43:24,060 --> 00:43:26,100
You know when to yield and when not.

924
00:43:27,180 --> 00:43:28,220
You are not a common man.
